Reference molecules and datasets.

known_mpro_inhibitors.csv
    12 known SARS-CoV-2 Mpro inhibitors with SMILES, source, binding mode, notes.
    Used for:
      (a) Reward sanity check (plan Fix 2 validation: top decile gate).
      (b) Lead-optimization prompt seeds (plan Fix 8.2).
      (c) "Recovery" metric during analysis.
    NOTE: SMILES strings were hand-curated from literature. Before publication,
    cross-check each against ChEMBL / PubChem — a few are known to have
    isomerism or tautomer variants. Annotate any corrections here.

zinc_random.smi  (not committed; download separately)
    ~2000 random drug-like molecules from ZINC20's "drug-like" subset.
    Used as:
      (a) Background for the reward sanity check.
      (b) Lead-optimization prompt seeds (zinc_random provenance).

To fetch:
    curl -o zinc_random.smi 'https://files.docking.org/2D/BB/BBAB/BBAB.smi' | head -n 2000
    (or equivalent tranche; any "drug-like" subset works)
